1
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:37,439
Lately,

2
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:38,920
in your factory,

3
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:40,079
they are laying people off.

4
00:00:41,039 --> 00:00:43,479
Director Wu is close with Manager Liu.

5
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,240
You need to

6
00:00:44,399 --> 00:00:45,600
get on their good side

7
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:48,359
and hold onto your Iron Rice Bowl.

8
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:51,520
Mom, don't worry.

9
00:00:52,079 --> 00:00:52,960
As for work,

10
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:53,920
I have my own plans.

11
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,439
You can't be careless about this.

12
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:58,439
You're good at everything,

13
00:00:58,759 --> 00:01:00,520
but you don't know how to socialize.

14
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,600
They are your leaders.

15
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:03,439
I'm just

16
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,359
afraid they'll have a bad impression of you

17
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,799
and it will affect your future.

18
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:14,920
Mom.

19
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:19,439
Here is 5,000 yuan.

20
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,200
5,000 yuan?

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:24,879
Where did it come from?

22
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:28,079
I fixed a machine for a factory.

23
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:31,040
The boss there gave me 10,000 yuan.

24
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,480
I used that money

25
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,680
to pay off the debts Dad left behind.

26
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,040
The remaining part,

27
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:39,000
I'm giving to you.

28
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,000
So much money...

29
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:44,079
You earned it all yourself?

30
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,439
My son is so capable now.

31
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,760
Mom,

32
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,799
there's something I want to tell you.

33
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:00,239
Hello, who is this?

34
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,000
Cousin.

35
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,280
Director Zhen.

36
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:10,960
Director Zhen,

37
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,000
hello.

38
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,520
This is Xiao Wu.

39
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:16,080
I heard Minjiang was demoted.

40
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,599
What is going on?

41
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,599
How did you know about that?

42
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,599
Don't ask me how I know.

43
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:23,960
I'm asking you,

44
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:26,080
what right do you have

45
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,919
to demote a Grade-8 Worker?

46
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,639
Director Zhen, it's a misunderstanding.

47
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:31,919
It was Zheng Minjiang who violated factory rules,

48
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:33,240
privately fixed machines for others,

49
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,039
and even hit his leader.

50
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:38,199
I just demoted him

51
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:40,280
to make him reflect,

52
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,439
to give him a chance to admit his mistake.

53
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,719
Have you actually investigated this clearly?

54
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,919
Uh, there shouldn't be a mistake.

55
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,879
What do you mean "shouldn't"?

56
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:52,080
Have Zheng Minjiang call me back.

57
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:53,280
Yes, yes, yes.

58
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,759
I will definitely find him tomorrow

59
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,680
and investigate properly again.

60
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,639
Please rest assured.

61
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,960
That Zheng Minjiang and Director Zhen,

62
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,159
what exactly is their relationship?

63
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:09,479
How did he alert Director Zhen?

64
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,680
Director Zhen thinks highly of him.

65
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,120
He called me many times before.

66
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,120
It seems that kid

67
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:18,680
is valued by Director Zhen.

68
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,520
Then offending Zheng Minjiang

69
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,479
is equivalent to offending Director Zhen, isn't it?

70
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,120
Should we

71
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,639
restore Zheng Minjiang's position?

72
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,639
We can't restore it.

73
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,000
If we chicken out,

74
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,039
he won't respect us at all in the future.

75
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:34,840
We

76
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,919
will just keep him stuck in the factory.

77
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,840
As long as he's under our noses,

78
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:41,000
he can't possibly rebel.

79
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,000
Alright.

80
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:46,680
Cousin,

81
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,120
I'll listen to you completely.

82
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:58,120
You two are even earlier than me.

83
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,919
It's all because of Second Brother.

84
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,560
I...

85
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,719
Didn't I say last night to work hard?

86
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,560
Of course, I can't fall behind my big brother.

87
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,759
We definitely have to be early.

88
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,039
The grain isn't enough, I'll go get some.

89
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,599
Okay.

90
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,279
There's a problem with the grain.

91
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,000
Why is the grain all moldy?

92
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,480
You guys check the others.

93
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,519
We can't use any of this batch.

94
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,160
I'm sorry.

95
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:48,920
I didn't check it properly.

96
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,639
Wait, no.

97
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,439
The ones on top are fine.

98
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,759
But the ones hidden underneath are moldy.

99
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,439
Someone definitely did this on purpose.

100
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,160
This grain...

101
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:00,920
Where did you buy it?

102
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,199
Wu Xiaojun's grain shop.

103
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,680
Wu Xiaojun?

104
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,360
He's Director Wu's brother.

105
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,600
And Li Guangming's cousin.

106
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,399
It must be because of Boss Tang.

107
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,480
They're doing this to get back at us.

108
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,959
I'm going to go find them.

109
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,040
Second Brother, don't be rash.

110
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,160
We already signed the receipts for the grain.

111
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:28,040
They won't admit to it if we go back now.

112
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:30,519
Maybe...

113
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,160
Sister Yingrong,

114
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,759
our delivery deadline...

115
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:34,240
...is coming up soon.

116
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:36,720
Why don't we just brew with this batch for now?

117
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:37,839
What are you saying?

118
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,360
How can we use this grain?

119
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:40,680
Even if we lose money,

120
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,000
we can't use this batch.

121
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,040
We should go to Big Brother about this.

122
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,040
Big Brother will know what to do.

123
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,040
No way.

124
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,319
We can't let your Big Brother...

125
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,600
...get involved with the vinegar factory again.

126
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:50,839
Why not?

127
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,720
Boss Tang has his eye on Zheng Minjiang now.

128
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,680
He wants him as a Technical Consultant at the factory.

129
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,399
Besides,

130
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,360
for him to leave the cement factory,

131
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,800
he still needs Director Wu's approval.

132
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,800
Who knows if he'll make trouble for him?

133
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,120
So what do we do?

134
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:04,800
Your Second Brother and I will take the receipt and go.

135
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,560
You stay here and check everything else.

136
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:07,759
Make sure there are no other issues.

137
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:08,600
Let's go.

138
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:14,959
What?

139
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:18,480
You want to quit the factory and go to a private company?

140
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:19,639
That's right.

141
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,120
I've thought about it for a long time.

142
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,399
Mom.

143
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,120
I haven't dared to tell you.

144
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,240
Actually, a while ago...

145
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:29,199
I was transferred to the Transport Workshop.

146
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:33,439
A perfectly good Grade-8 Worker...

147
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:35,879
Sent to do hard labor.

148
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,319
That won't do.

149
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,160
Let's go, let's go.

150
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:39,360
Let's go find your leaders.

151
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,319
Let's go.

152
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:41,920
Mom.

153
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:43,839
Don't get so worked up.

154
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,680
Our factory isn't doing too well right now.

155
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,279
And they're laying people off.

156
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:51,079
I want to take advantage of Boss Tang's appreciation...

157
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,319
Rely on my skills...

158
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,959
And find a good path forward.

159
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:57,199
State-owned enterprises are an Iron Rice Bowl.

160
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,000
Private companies won't take care of you for life.

161
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:04,439
The private economy is the direction of the future.

162
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:07,839
I should have been like Wang Yingrong long ago...

163
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,680
And gone out on my own.

164
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,399
I've already wasted so much time.

165
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:12,160
I shouldn't miss this opportunity again.

166
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,800
That homewrecker Wang Yingrong...

167
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:15,680
She's got you again...

168
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,839
Big Brother, I...

169
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,920
What's wrong?

170
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:20,839
I...

171
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,439
I have something to discuss with Big Brother.

172
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:26,720
Mom.

173
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:28,399
About resigning...

174
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,759
I've already decided.

175
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,240
Wang Yingrong.

176
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:37,600
Minjiang.

177
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,199
No way.

178
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:42,519
I need to find a new wife for Minjiang.

179
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,439
Wu Xiaojun!

180
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,480
Get out here!

181
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,399
Wu Xiaojun!

182
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:49,879
Where is Wu Xiaojun?

183
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,519
Isn't this Wang Yingrong and Zheng's second son?

184
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,279
What are you doing here?

185
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,959
The grain your cousin sold us has problems.

186
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:56,600
Where is he?

187
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,519
Xiaojun went out to restock.

188
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,360
He's not here.

189
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,040
What did you just say?

190
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,000
Our family's grain has problems?

191
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,680
Do you have evidence?

192
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:09,519
If you dare ruin our family's reputation...

193
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,720
I'll take you to court.

194
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,680
This is the receipt your brother gave us.

195
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,000
Do you still dare deny it?

196
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,879
Don't you know grain is non-refundable once it leaves?

197
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:24,199
I think you deliberately took some moldy grain...

198
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,240
To frame us.

199
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,199
You expect us to compensate you?

200
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,439
You still won't admit it?

201
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,639
I don't believe it.

202
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,480
That Wu Xiaojun isn't in the shop.

203
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,240
I'm going to find him.

204
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:34,360
Is this a kidnapping or a robbery in broad daylight?

205
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:38,120
I heard you were just released from prison.

206
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,879
Someone like you with a criminal record...

207
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,679
Dares to cause trouble again after getting out.

208
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,159
You...

209
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,240
Don't be impulsive.

210
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:54,080
The way I see it...

211
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,960
You came to our shop deliberately to pick a fight.

212
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,440
And try to extort us.

213
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,639
Since you started it...

214
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,519
Even if I have someone break your legs...

215
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,960
It would be self-defense.

216
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:05,840
Men!

217
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,039
Close the doors and beat the dogs!

218
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:14,279
Stay back.

219
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,639
Leave me alone.

220
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,159
Help!

221
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,000
Why are you here?

222
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,440
Zheng Minjiang.

223
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,600
What? Trying to be a hero?

224
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,960
Come on, then.

225
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,480
If you dare touch me,

226
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
I'll have you kicked out of the factory tomorrow.

227
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,559
Haiyang.

228
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,639
I don't really care.

229
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,399
But you know as well as I do,

230
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:47,720
Manager Liu

231
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,240
hates people who cause trouble for him

232
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,759
and ruin the factory's reputation.

233
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,200
Director Wu,

234
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,480
if today...

235
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,600
us brothers beat you up right here,

236
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:00,399
then we'll all get fired together.

237
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,399
Are you threatening me?

238
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,399
I'm your superior!

239
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:06,919
We're not at the factory right now.

240
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,120
You're no superior here.

241
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,279
You...

242
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,360
I'm in a good mood today,

243
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,559
so I'll let you off the hook.

244
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,679
I won't stoop to your level.

245
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,840
You guys can go.

246
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,159
Let's go.

247
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,600
Seriously, what were you thinking?

248
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,679
Something this big happens and you don't tell me?

249
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:43,799
Brother,

250
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,440
Yingrong was afraid it would affect you.

251
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,360
And you,

252
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:49,240
the way Wu Youcai was acting just now,

253
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,960
he was obviously waiting for you to show up

254
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,399
so you'd hit him

255
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,200
and he'd have something on you.

256
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:54,440
You've already made one mistake.

257
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,559
Why can't you change

258
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,639
that impulsive temper of yours?

259
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,840
Let's go.

260
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,879
I can walk myself.

261
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,679
Move it, let's go.

262
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,120
You're usually quite the talker.

263
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,679
Why so quiet now?

264
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,480
You're so reckless now.

265
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:21,159
Why do they have to be such bullies?

266
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:24,600
I sank all my money into this.

267
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,320
It's just not fair!

268
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,720
I just want to do one thing right.

269
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:30,000
Why is it so hard?

270
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,200
What are you looking at?

271
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:34,279
Never seen a girl cry before?

272
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,000
Money...

273
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,000
About the money,

274
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,519
you don't need to worry about it.

275
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,679
I still have some.

276
00:11:54,039 --> 00:11:55,000
If that's not enough,

277
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:57,600
I can ask Boss Tang for an advance on my wages.

278
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:02,120
But for you to go to Boss Tang,

279
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,639
you need Director Wu's approval.

280
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,639
If he sabotages you,

281
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,720
what will you do?

282
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:11,440
Don't worry about me.

283
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,120
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

284
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,360
Stop crying.

285
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:21,039
I know you'd help me this time,

286
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,080
but...

287
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:27,879
I want to figure it out myself.

288
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:43,840
Come in.

289
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,279
Manager Liu,

290
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:49,559
you wanted to see me?

291
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,840
I heard from Director Wu a couple of days ago

292
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,240
that you violated factory regulations,

293
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,519
so you were demoted.

294
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:55,440
Manager Liu,

295
00:12:56,039 --> 00:12:57,120
I didn't violate any regulations.

296
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,080
I went out after working hours.

297
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,080
Besides...

298
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:01,840
No need to explain.

299
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,039
Regarding that matter,

300
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:04,720
Director Zhen has personally investigated it.

301
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,360
What Director Wu reported

302
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,679
does not violate factory regulations.

303
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,840
Mr. Zhen...

304
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:13,799
What did you say?

305
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:16,279
Nothing.

306
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,519
Thank you, Manager Liu.

307
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,080
As the manager,

308
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,639
letting my staff suffer such injustice...

309
00:13:22,639 --> 00:13:24,720
I bear some responsibility for this too.

310
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,720
If you really want to thank someone,

311
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:28,600
you should thank Director Zhen.

312
00:13:30,759 --> 00:13:32,279
I don't have Director Zhen's contact information.

313
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,879
His number is right here.

314
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,519
Have a good talk with Director Zhen.

315
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:43,559
Thank you, Manager Liu.

316
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,279
You're welcome.

317
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,679
Hello.

318
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,279
Hello? Mr. Zhen?

319
00:14:01,879 --> 00:14:02,720
This is Zheng Minjiang.

320
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,320
Minjiang.

321
00:14:04,919 --> 00:14:06,639
I finally got a hold of you.
